author: rhuijben
msg: Use a single query to determine which records need their moved_to updated
during delete. This should handle many issues currently not covered by tests
where moves are not stored in the highest op-depth.
(delete_node): Don't perform unnecessary double allocation. Remove specific
query for special directory case. Process all moved descendants in one
